headline: Baker Hughes, Woodside Energy collaborate on small-scale decarbonisation solutions
summary: The Net Power platform offers low-cost, low-emission power generation with near-total CO₂ capture.

headline: Baker Hughes, Woodside Advance Net Power Decarbonization Plan
summary: BKR and Woodside Energy are expanding their partnership to develop a small-scale, low-carbon power solution using Net Power's platform to reduce emissions in oil, gas and heavy industries.
